<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٥٤- عَبد اللهِ بْن الرهين.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>سَمِع ابْن الزُّبَير، قَولَهُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ ابنُ عُيَينَةَ:</span> سألني سُفيان بْن سَعِيد عَنْهُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>سَمّاه علي.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ غيره:</span> أُراه النَّضر بن رهين.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>